<br>
Some folks in the guild (predominantly folks that came from dkp guilds) aren't thrilled about this. Most folks in the guild, though, are happy with it.<br>
<br>
What are some opinions here? I know I can't make everyone happy, and I'm not in a big hurry to change over to dkp just to please a few newcomers, but as we get higher (most of the mains are 50+ and some are 60+ at this point), we have a hard time finding new warriors and clerics because of the draw of gear a &quot;raiding guild&quot; could provide. <p>Baron Wiltan Ryouki<br>
