<br>
A major problem is that the game contains the wrong balance of loot.  For example, in the Velious expansion, significantly more melee loot drops than caster loot, and the caster loot itself is much less of an upgrade than the melee loot.  It's only in Luclin and beyond that this imbalance is corrected; and in PoP, the pendulum swings perhaps a little too far the other way, with casters doing rather better than melees (apart from the knights, of course, who seem to do very well indeed from PoP boss itemization).<br>
<br>
So even if you get the points values completely right - an impossible task of itself - you still won't have completely fair loot distribution.  That's just how it is.<br>
<br>
